org.apache.juneau

Class ConfigApply<T extends Annotation>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.ConfigApply<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The annotation that this ConfigApply reads from.
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BeanConfigApply, ConfigApply.NoOp, CsvConfigApply, HtmlConfigApply, HtmlDocConfigApply, JsoConfigApply, JsonConfigApply, JsonSchemaConfigApply, MsgPackConfigApply, OpenApiConfigApply, ParserConfigApply, PlainTextConfigApply, RdfConfigApply, RestConfigApply, RestMethodConfigApply, RestResourceConfigApply, SerializerConfigApply, SoapXmlConfigApply, UonConfigApply, UrlEncodingConfigApply, XmlConfigApply

    public abstract class ConfigApply<T extends Annotation>
extends Object
    Class used to add properties to a PropertyStore from an annotation (e.g. BeanConfig).
